      "writtenOn": "2026-06-30T06:01:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Good catch. I added a setClockLimitReadbackPending flag — only the post-set read-back clears the in-flight gate, periodic polls leave it untouched. The error paths (and the case where no read-back can be sent) clear the gate too, so a failed set can\u0027t wedge it shut.",
      "parentUuid": "59c205be_cbb20933",
